<div class="relative mt-12">
  <div class="relative text-center pt-32 pb-16 z-10" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(58, 0, 93, 0.78) 6.52%, #23698F 98.04%);">
    <div class="container mx-auto inline-block my-24">
      <h1 class="mb-2 mx-auto inline-block">
        <span class="uppercase text-white">EmberJS Chennai Chapter</span>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <div class="text-3xl text-amber-light inline-block float-left font-normal">9th November 2019</div>
        <div class="text-3xl text-amber-light inline-block float-right font-normal">Freshworks, Chennai, IN</div>
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <a class="btn primary-btn mb-24" href="https://www.meetup.com/EmberJS-Chennai/events/265579607/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      RSVP for meetup
    </a>
  </div>
  <img class="absolute pin-b" src="assets/images/hero-bg.svg" style="bottom: -8rem" />
  <div class="absolute pin-b h-32 z-10 w-full bg-auto bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url('assets/images/polygon.png'); bottom: -4rem"></div>
</div>

<div class="mt-12 w-screen">
  <div class="container mx-auto p-5 text-xl">
    <p class="mb-5">
      Hello Chennai,
    </p>
    <p>
      We look forward to our second EmberJS meet-up on November 9th, 2019 (Saturday).
      Join us at Freshworks office at 9 AM for some amazing talks.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

